                            <h2 class="text-brand">Visit Zakopane</h2>
                            <p>
                                <span itemprop="articlebody">
                                    This was our second visit to <strong>Zakopane</strong> since we arrive in Poland in
                                    2019. The first
                                    one was in December with the idea to go skiing, but this one we did it on the 22 of
                                    August to 2020 to visit <strong>Lake Morskie Oko</strong>. It was just a weekend
                                    trip just perfect
                                    for what we want it to do. We stay on the <a
                                        href="http://apartamentyzakopianskietarasy.pl/" title="Zakopianskie Tarasy"
                                        rel="external"> Zakopianskie Tarasy</a> apartments. The place
                                    is just beautiful, with one of the most beautiful views of the majestic peaks fo
                                    the
                                    <em>Tatra Mountains</em>. They are located just a 5-minute walk to the famous
                                    <em>Krupowki
                                        street</em>
                                    in which you can find a variety of shops and restaurants. Children friendly
                                    place
                                    since it has a playground where the kid can have fun. Definitely a place we will
                                    stay again if we return

                                    back to visit <strong>Zakopane</strong> in the future.
                                </span>
                            </p>


                            <img class="post-img img-responsive text-center"
