                            <h3 class="text-brand">Smacznego!</h3>
                            <p>
                                As a final note, I will need to say that <strong>Zakopane</strong> has other interesting
                                things to do
                                with kids, like going to the pools. Definitely is a place where you can have a lot of
                                fun.
                            </p>

